Leslie: I wish I could help. One of those things bit my leg.

Zoe: We'll take care of it. It will be a simple matter.
Zoe: You just stay alive. I can't lose you.

Leslie: Zoe, I'll be fine. I've been in my fair share of scrapes. You know that.
<<char_hide Leslie 0.5 false>>
<<char_show Eden 0.5 false>>

Fuyumi: If you wish, I may assist with defeating these monsters.


Eden: Yeah! I can help, too!

<<char_show Lana 0.5>>
<<char_show Aspen 0.5>>
Lana: We can all help you, Zoe. We can stop the corruption together!

Zoe: ...
Zoe: ...Fine.

